name: D/B Black-ON-Black V1 Fuel Filter Tuck Kit
description:
Our Fuel Tuck'd Fuel Filter Kit allows you to convert your stock fuel line and filter to AN braided line and inline filter. It is the easiest kit to install on the market,NO flaring needed! Our kit consist of black braided hose,  Fuel Tuck'd Black 40 micron inline filter, and all back AN fittings needed to adapt to your factory fuel lines. Our kit comes with the AN fittings to adapt to your fuel rail, feed line.   
This Kit is available for:
              1988-2000 Honda Civic
              1990-2001 Acura Integra 

**PLEASE CHECK OUR EMAIL WITHIN 24 HOURS OF ORDERING TO ANSWER A FEW QUESTIONS SO WE CAN PROCESS YOUR ORDER** We ask for 3-5 business days to process orders** 

V1 Kit Includes everything for the fuel feed line

name: S2000 Clutch Master Cylinder Kit
description:
S2000 clutch master cylinder with spacer to give your bay that "tucked" look! When our spacer is used there is no need for re-threading the rod on the master cylinder. It is direct bolt on! 

We now offer the complete kit! S2000 Clutch master cylinder,spacer, and clutch line! 

These are direct bolt on for:

1992-2000 Honda Civic
1994-2001 Acura Integra
